monogr.title: Myotomia Reformata: Or, A New Administration of All the Muscles of Humane Bodies; Wherein the true Uses of the Muscles are Explained, the Errors of former Anatomists concerning Them Confuted, and several Muscles not hitherto taken notice of Described; To which are subjoin'd, A Graphical Description of the Bones; And other Anatomical Observations.
